Foot-and-mouth disease, Korea (Dem. People's Rep.)
--------------------------------------------------
Information received on [and dated] 24 Mar 2014 from Mr Ri Kyong Gun, Director of the Veterinary and, Ministry of Agriculture, Anti-Epizootic Department, Pyongyang, Korea (Dem. People's Rep.)

Summary
Report type: follow-up report no 1
Date of start of the event: 8 Jan 2014
Date of pre-confirmation of the event: 8 Jan 2014
Report date: 24 Mar 2014
Date submitted to OIE: 24 Mar 2014
Reason for notification: reoccurrence of a listed disease
Date of previous occurrence: April 2011
Manifestation of disease: clinical disease
Causal agent: Foot and mouth disease virus
Serotype: O
Nature of diagnosis: laboratory (advanced)
This event pertains to the whole country

